column1:
Didi is winning Nandigram. The question of her fighting from another seat doesn't arise. 
@narendramodi
 Ji, retract from your efforts to mislead people before they see your lies with the end of nomination in WB. Look for a safer seat in 2024, as you will be challenged in Varanasi.

Today, in the presence of National General Secretary 
@abhishekaitc
 and RS MP 
@derekobrienmp
, former Union Minister and sitting MP 
@SuPriyoBabul
 joined the Trinamool family.

We take this opportunity to extend a very warm welcome to him!

Ek akela kitno pe bhari para, 
@narendramodi
 ji?
